{"tid":608615,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【青委會】最年輕委員 18歲鄭康煥網上多次反佔中","createTime":"2018-03-28T09:55:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T07:45:30.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"8d9416544a64b1bac16aec5b51444d09ffdce15e","tid":608615,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:55:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180328/large/1522228258_20a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180328%2Flarge%2F1522228258_20a2.jpg&h=9d53f1d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180328/large/1522228260_3863.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180328%2Flarge%2F1522228260_3863.jpg&h=b3f1b474&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府今日公佈青年發展委員會名單中，當中年紀最輕的是透過自薦計劃獲委任的科大一年級生、主修環球中國研究的鄭康煥。《蘋果》綜合網上資料，年僅18歲的鄭康煥兩個月前開始youtube頻道講賽馬，節目內容透露其家人是馬主，小學已開始留意賽馬，目前在報章有賽馬專欄。2014年雨傘運動其間鄭亦曾在facebook發表意見，包括多次分享「反佔中，保普選，撐警察大聯盟」專頁的內容，並曾發表帖文指「佔中比八號波還要勁」、「學生無罪，但佔中有罪」等。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》找到疑似鄭康煥的facebook，顯示他畢業於聖公會鄧肇堅中學，現於科大就讀，主修環球中國研究。鄭亦有「上莊」，參與科大學生會飲食藝術及文化學會的幹事會選舉。<br />\n<br />\n青年發展委員會是首個透過青年委員自薦試行計劃招募並委任青年委員的政府委員會。政務司司長張建宗指，三名委員經過嚴謹的甄選程序，從503名合資格申請者中脫穎而出，展現了無比的決心和熱誠投入委員會的工作。<br />\n<br />\n另外，委員之一精神科醫生葉沛霖指，早前曾與民政事務局代表見面，交流對青年發展的看法，對獲委任為青年事務委員會委員感榮幸。他說，期望建立渠道讓青年表達意見，令政府了解他們的需要和困難，在政策層面配合，例如樓價、租金高企下如何滿足住屋需求，以及上流機會等，「見到年青人其實願意去講，好似社交媒體，都會分享睇法，希望有正式少少渠道畀佢哋表達」。他認為年青人關心社會，「唔好嘥咗佢哋嘅諗法」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180328/58006199\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180328%2F58006199&d=0T8ksHthJx%2B4TlHDq%2BQ8N7r9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=eef8f609\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180328%2F58006199&h=a1a2bca6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180328/58006199</a>"},{"pid":"80f8a29fc7db0b3e3b71521dd52e79cd36608656","tid":608615,"uid":155095,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:56:13.000Z","msg":"有前途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e06c2c4a8d11038ab9038f433c38ad4a33d630c","tid":608615,"uid":38671,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:56:36.000Z","msg":"家人是馬主，反佔中<br />\n明白哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d86ebfdc63a265f8c10b6c61bb0adfb8f27d7db","tid":608615,"uid":21917,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:57:52.000Z","msg":"估到啦 同當年皇族內閣一樣"},{"pid":"323141dd7829d1c3ed629f8c420e8da123a22430","tid":608615,"uid":6799,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"5e06c2c4a8d11038ab9038f433c38ad4a33d630c","tid":608615,"uid":38671,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:56:36.000Z","msg":"家人是馬主，反佔中<br />\n明白哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 既得利益者"},{"pid":"bdfaf04fbd7cfcbb241863708066d85fe9b0dcc5","tid":608615,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:59:12.000Z","msg":"預撚左架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"293a3d4602a01ce8fb569f32e152122d5a7886a6","tid":608615,"uid":26506,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:59:59.000Z","msg":"Major Global China Studies 上到位梗係唔妥啦"},{"pid":"c68a77b13a4e225573c790a5691547c5369b784d","tid":608615,"uid":38671,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T10:01:01.000Z","msg":"林鄭仲話聆聽年輕人聲音<br />\n係呀，有錢仔既聲音嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95567e72c0864